originalText.text: I had the most amazing experience working alongside CNM Angela. Her ability to bring a sense of calm and reassurance to not only my client but to everyone in the entire room was inspiring. As a birth doula is such a blessing to team up with the medical staff that makes the birthing person and her support feel safe , acknowledged, respected, and cared for. I am so grateful to meet Angela and learn from her as well.

originalText.text: Angela is a compassionate, patient, and incredibly kind healer.  It's easy to see she cares about her patients and loves what she does. Angela and the entire staff are welcoming and put you at ease from the moment you walk into the office. She is thorough and takes time to listen, offering thoughtful diagnostic solutions and treatment plans. If you are looking for a warm , thoughtful  provider, look no further.  I'm so grateful for her.
